main event: A witness in Memphis, Tennessee reported seeing multiple unidentified flying objects in the night sky on December 27, 1960.
interesting points: The witness reported seeing 3-12 objects in the sky for 9-10 seconds.
The objects were moving in an east-north direction.
The witness did not hear any sound from the objects.
The objects appeared as a bright white light, and were estimated to cover about half the size of a match head held at arm's length.
The objects disappeared behind some trees and then reappeared, indicating they were able to move behind and in front of objects.
sighted object: multiple unidentified flying objects, described as bright white lights
